23
00:03:10,478 --> 00:03:11,859
You wear emotions.

24
00:03:15,018 --> 00:03:16,899
Evoking emotions.

25
00:03:17,819 --> 00:03:19,639
That's what fashion is all about.

26
00:03:22,788 --> 00:03:24,609
